Description: This is a discontinued Taylor T5z. Beautifully visual quilted maple. Comes with original Taylor T5z hardshell case Serial #1111245142 Bought for the convenience of acoustic/electric capability but have come to the realization that I never play electric so this gorgeous guitar simply sits inside its case. From Taylor Website- T5z Pro-QM LTD A quilted maple top brings a striking visual flair to this limited edition T5z Pro. Clear finish preserves the figured wood’s naturally creamy complexion, while black binding outlines the guitar’s contours, including the sapele hollowbody’s f-holes. Unique T5z features include a more compact body than the original T5, plus a 12-inch fretboard radius and jumbo frets, which together provide a familiar feel for electric players. Like the T5, the T5z is equipped with a three-pickup configuration of an acoustic body sensor, a concealed neck humbucker, and a visible bridge humbucker, plus five-way switching and onboard tone controls, giving players an incredibly versatile electric/acoustic guitar. Additional details include nickel hardware and a Spires inlay scheme. A universe of fabulous electric and acoustic sounds - in 1 seamless instrument! Gorgeous quilted maple top looks great Compact body will feel comfortable for solidbody electric players Hollowbody design with active soundboard for natural acoustic tone Smooth-playing ebony fingerboard with jumbo frets lets you shred in comfort 24.875" scale length, 12" fingerboard radius, and fat frets make for effortless string bending Versatile T5z electronics with 5-way switch Acoustic body sensor, concealed neck humbucker, visible bridge humbucker Taylor chrome tuners Taylor hardshell case included
Title: Taylor T5z Pro-QM Ltd Quilted Maple
